line_1: Who banters vice with friendly jokes,
Who gap'd to catch Jack-Pudding's jokes.
line_2: They forc'd their way through draggled folks,

line_1: And unco tales, an' funnie jokes,
line_2: Wi' merry sangs, an' friendly cracks,

line_1: Were made the butt of vulgar jokes;
line_2: That PATRIOTS now, like other folks,

line_1: And seasons his Whifs with impertinent Jokes.
line_2: Four Pipes after Dinner he constantly smokes;
